cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a novel cooperative system for UAV and UGV, which involves autonomous navigation, mapping, and obstacle avoidance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also employs visual inertial navigation and 3D voxel mapping, which falls under the sub-categories cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also presents an autonomous framework for collaborative navigation, which involves path planning and traversability analysis, falling under the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
